WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.900 --> 00:00:05.100
Which game are you most looking forward to the most?

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:23.900
Every game, everyone. Because I think everyone is going to be important for me. I have to do well in every game because I think this season can be a very good season for me, very important season for me.

00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.001
Who poses the biggest threat this season?

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:39.001
Of course we have difficult teams to compete with us but we try to beat them and of course to win the league.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:50.001
Usually itís always Chelsea but this season I think itís probably going to be different. Weíll see.

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:51.300
Competition for places

00:00:51.700 --> 00:01:07.700
