00:01:08.001 --> 00:01:09.600
What targets have you set yourself?

00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:40.600
Of course I want to do much more and I want to help my team to win this time because last year we were disappointed and we want to do better in the Championís League and the league. But my target is of course, I know what I did so well in the last part of the season and I want to do better.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:43.200
Which league is the best to watch?

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:47.300
Premier League first and then after Spain.

00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:49.700
Who will win Serie A?

00:01:50.001 --> 00:01:53.700
Maybe Inter again, they have a good team.

00:01:54.001 --> 00:01:56.400
Who will win the Milan Derby?

00:01:56.700 --> 00:02:01.100
We never know, itís always difficult to know the game.

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:04.300
