00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:21.600
Who will win El Clasico?

00:02:21.900 --> 00:02:36.001
Last year I was confident on Barca because the way they played was fantastic and then they show everything on the pitch, they win the both games. But this year maybe it can be different.

